parameters:
Knight: The outskirts are completely
wiped out... There are no survivors...

Zerachiel: No, it seems like we can't
proceed any further.
PushGab 4 天使をやっつけないとっ！！
Zerachiel: Lala!? Why are you here!?

Lala: Oh, if it isn't my eternal best
friend Zerachiel, I thought someone else
had come to rescue me!

Zerachiel: We've become best friends
without even realizing it...

Zerachiel: No, not just that! Lala was
also attacked!?

Lala: Actually, I was originally a
member of the choir and a close aide to
the Archangel.

Lala: That Archangel went missing, and
I've been searching for them all this
time.

Lala: And then the angels attacked,
saying Eliminate the rebel!...!!

Lala: I was just... searching for the
Archangel!!

Zerachiel: Actually, it seems like my
life is also being targeted.

Zerachiel: It's dangerous to act alone
now that it's come to this.

Lala: I completely agree!! Let me act
together with you!!

Lala: By the way, I wonder if the castle
is okay?

Zerachiel: Let's go and see how things
are.
